1.Sir walter releighs colony at Roanoke Island was <br>
absorbed by the indians.<br>
2. The origional spanish settlement at St . Augustine florida<br>
was killed by the indians.<br>
3. The viking colony of Vineland that was established at<br>
in Ad  1029 was lost to an unknown fate.<br>
<br>
4. The Plymouth colony of the puritans was saved by the indians.<br>
